WEBVTT

00:02.435 --> 00:04.426
Do you think
a little girl like Abagail...

00:04.504 --> 00:07.234
could be capable of murder?

00:07.307 --> 00:10.936
It was you who killed her, Abagail!
I didn't kill her!

00:11.011 --> 00:13.946
I'm coming!

00:14.014 --> 00:16.539
Sam, look out!

00:24.557 --> 00:28.550
<i>You two rabbits ought to be ashamed!</i>

00:28.628 --> 00:30.528
<i>The weddin'is tomorrow.!</i>

00:30.597 --> 00:33.088
You get him out of here.
You hear me, Abigail Fuller?

00:33.166 --> 00:35.464
Don Takins's boy's disappeared.

00:35.535 --> 00:37.935
<i>It looks like you're gonna have
a witch hunt on your hands.</i>

00:38.004 --> 00:41.030
Sam, look out!

00:41.107 --> 00:44.702
No! No!
She should die! No!

00:44.778 --> 00:48.976
Just know that
for this brief moment in time,

00:49.049 --> 00:51.347
we belong to each other.

00:52.419 --> 00:54.580
Please know that.

00:56.222 --> 00:58.213
I love you.

